# DockAccessory.TrackedSubjectType

**Enumeration**

The subjects that the dock can track.

## Declaration

```swift
enum TrackedSubjectType
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **DockAccessory.TrackedSubjectType.object(_:)**: Tracked subject contains an object.
- **DockAccessory.TrackedSubjectType.person(_:)**: Tracked subject contains a person.
